author: NEW YORK DAILY NEWS
title: Carey Mulligan reveals she welcomed baby girl
text:
Carey Mulligan has confirmed reports that she and her rocker hubby Marcus Mumford have welcomed their first child .
“It’s a girl and she's three weeks old,” the actress said Monday on the U.K. gabfest “The Graham Norton Show.”
The actress confirmed the news just a week after she made her first red carpet appearance since giving birth at the London Film Festival for a screening of her new film “Suffragette.”
West Ian/West Ian/PA Photos/ABACA Carey Mulligan revealed she and her husband Marcus Mumford welcomed a baby girl during an appearance on “The Graham Norton Show.” Enlarge Ray Tamarra/Getty Images Carey Mulligan and singer Marcus Mumford leave an after party at the Ukrainian Institute of America in 2012. Enlarge
Mulligan and Mumford, who tied the knot in 2012, are known for keeping their personal life under wraps, and did not confirm they were expecting while she was pregnant.
"Marcus is the only thing that's mine that I can keep totally away," she explained in the May issue of Vogue on why she keeps her marriage private. "So I try to."
